{"componentChunkName":"component---theme-src-templates-post-template-jsx","path":"/post/launch-sublime-text-from-command-line/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>1.添加 link</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">ln</span> -s /Applications/Sublime<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span> Text.app/Contents/SharedSupport/bin/subl /usr/local/bin/subl</code></pre></div>\n<p>2.编辑 PATH</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">vim</span> ~/.bash_profile</code></pre></div>\n<p>3.添加 PATH</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token builtin class-name\">export</span> <span class=\"token assign-left variable\"><span class=\"token environment constant\">PATH</span></span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span>/usr/local/bin:<span class=\"token environment constant\">$PATH</span></code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">esc -<span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token builtin class-name\">shift</span> + <span class=\"token builtin class-name\">:</span> -<span class=\"token operator\">></span> wq保存退出</code></pre></div>\n<p>4.应用</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token builtin class-name\">source</span> ~/.bash_profile</code></pre></div>","excerpt":"1.添加 link 2.编辑 PATH 3.添加 PATH 4.应用","frontmatter":{"date":"05月09, 2015","title":"Mac OS 终端使用 subl 运行 Sublime Text 3","tags":["macOS","Sublime","Editor"]}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/post/launch-sublime-text-from-command-line/","prev":null,"next":{"slug":"/post/mongodb-command/","title":"mongoDB 常用命令"}}}}